{"tid":2324594,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC/PS/Xbox] Cyberpunk 2077 集中討論區(11)","createTime":"2020-12-14T05:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T16:33:52.000Z","uid":59819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"3003e46084fc487eca04ec61f9aaf58d347cf78f","tid":2324594,"uid":59819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><p class=\"center\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGkqvGx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGkqvGx.jpg&h=77395dc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n動作冒險開放世界《電馭叛客 2077》將讓你深入沉溺於肉體改造、爭權奪利又紙醉金迷的巨型都市「夜城」。化身非法傭兵 V，尋找某種絕無僅有的植入物，掌握長生不死的關鍵。自由打造角色的生化改造裝置、技能及遊玩風格，並盡情探索一望無際的巨型城市，讓每一次抉擇逐步左右劇情與世界的走向。<br />\n<br />\nTrailer:<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n\t</p><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ixl31324UxE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fixl31324UxE&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725JNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=e56ecced\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ixl31324UxE</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BO8lX3hDU30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBO8lX3hDU30&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725JNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=e72c3ebb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BO8lX3hDU30</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UnA7tepsc7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUnA7tepsc7s&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725JNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=d60c0a41\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UnA7tepsc7s</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發售日: <br />\n<span class=\"medium\"><del>2020年4月16日<br />\n2020年9月17日<br />\n2020年11月19日</del></span><br />\n2020年12月10日<br />\n<br />\n夜城(Night City)網站<br />\